Revision history for Perl extension Win32::Locale
                                        Time-stamp: "2004-01-11 18:55:22 AST"

2004-01-11  Sean M. Burke  sburke@cpan.org

        * Release 0.04 -- Merely fixed a potential "use of uninitialized
	value" warning when calling get_locale or get_language on
	non-MSWin systems.
	
2003-07-16  Sean M. Burke  sburke@cpan.org

	* Release 0.03 -- changes *-latin to the now-standard *-latn;
	ditto *-cyrillic to *-cyrl.
	Changed "<SRB> <Serbian> <Serbian (Cyrillic)>"'s langtag grom "sr"
	to "sr-cyrl".
	* Some incidental dist-making stuff (moving test.pl to t/*.t)
	
2001-05-17  Sean M. Burke  sburke@cpan.org

	* Release 0.02 -- corrects UK English from 'en-UK' to 'en-GB'
	
2001-05-16  Sean M. Burke  sburke@cpan.org

	* Release 0.01 -- first release

